Package com.hack23.cia.web.impl.ui.application.views.common.menufactory.api.text

package com.hack23.cia.web.impl.ui.application.views.common.menufactory.api.text
This package provides classes and interfaces for managing text-based menu items within the Citizen Intelligence Agency web application. Key classes and interfaces: - TextMenuItemFactory: Interface for creating text-based menu items. Dependencies and relationships: - Depends on com.hack23.cia.web.impl.ui.application.views.common.menufactory.api for menu factory interfaces. - Depends on com.vaadin.ui for Vaadin UI components.
